  "title": "Assistant Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Salary $3,500 -$4,500<br>\n</strong><br>\nLocation: 171 Kampong Ampat, KA Foodlink, #03-12 S (368330)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualification:</strong><br>\n- Diploma and above<br>\n- 2 years or more of relevant working experience.<br>\n- Good in English and Mandarin<br>\n- Only Singaporean/PR</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our Team is looking for a manager to generate sales, increase sales revenue, improve client relations, oversee and manage events, team leadership, and strategic planning.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Main roles and responsibilities</p>\n<p><br>\n- Sales generation, putting in new sales by discovering new prospects, reaching out to different industries to find B2B clients that require catering services; Increasing sales revenue by capturing recent sales and bringing in high-value clients.<br>\n- Event Management, supervise and assist in a buffet set up, ensuring all the buffet lines are set up according to the client's needs or event theme.<br>\n- Team Leader, build and maintain good work relations between all the staff, able to lead and delegate work.<br>\n- Bilingual, can speak and write in English and Chinese effectively due to the different group workers' backgrounds.<br>\n- Critical Thinking, able to come up with solutions and solve problems.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Working hours:</strong><br>\nMonday-Friday: 9:00 am-5:00 pm<br>\nSaturday: 9:00 am-1:00 pm</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For interested applicants, kindly send your resume and supporting documents to <a href=\"mailto:accounts@incntl.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\">accounts@incntl.com.sg</a></p>",
